Text: The ladies are great musicians, but this video is poor quality. The video is a single camera, shot without a tripod, from the side of the stage. The whole show is shown in a very shaky single shot. The audio quality is OK but not great. THis video is not worth the download.  For a music group that appears to have gone to the trouble to put on a good show, this video appears to be a total afterthought. Avoid downloading this.
